  "body": "The issue is for the following line:\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/zeppelin-solidity/blob/5cf503673faea92c1b5c615c3f8358febf06e160/contracts/token/StandardToken.sol#L81\r\n\r\nThe use of SafeMath adds the following check:\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/zeppelin-solidity/blob/f3867f847722b298c360a9a0158c7aa89c7d557c/contracts/math/SafeMath.sol#L23\r\n\r\nHowever, exactly that is checked right before:\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/zeppelin-solidity/blob/5cf503673faea92c1b5c615c3f8358febf06e160/contracts/token/StandardToken.sol#L78",
