    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I believe the check on line 78 exists because of line 79:\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/zeppelin-solidity/blob/5cf503673faea92c1b5c615c3f8358febf06e160/contracts/token/StandardToken.sol#L79\r\n\r\nIn a decrease function we don't want to throw an error here.  For instance, if _subtractedValue = 100 and oldValue = 50 then we want to oldValue to decrease to 0 and not decrease to -50 or throw an error.\r\n\r\nSee the tests:\r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/zeppelin-solidity/blob/f79f7b00e3266ae4a705c5a5400559721bd764ef/test/StandardToken.js#L103",
